---
// DevOps & Cloud Roadmap
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>DevOps & Cloud Roadmap</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style is:global>
:root {
  --bg:     #0c0e13;
  --bg1:    #111318;
  --bg2:    #181b22;
  --bg3:    #1e2229;
  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
  --border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.13);
  --text:   #d4d8e2;
  --muted:  #6b7280;
  --faint:  #3a3f4a;
  --orange: #f97316;
  --orange2:#fb923c;
  --orange-bg: rgba(249,115,22,0.08);
  --orange-border: rgba(249,115,22,0.25);
  --green:  #22c55e;
  --blue:   #38bdf8;
  --yellow: #fbbf24;
  --red:    #f87171;
  --mono:   'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  --body:   'Outfit', sans-serif;
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--body);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}

/* scan-line overlay */
body::after{
  content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;
  background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg,transparent,transparent 2px,rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 2px,rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 4px);
}
/* grid bg */
body::before{
  content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:40px 40px;
}

.site{position:relative;z-index:1}

.back-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 20px 40px 0;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 12px;
  transition: color 0.2s;
}
.back-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }

/* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg)}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--faint);border-radius:2px}

/* ── HEADER ── */
header{
  height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:0 40px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
  background:rgba(12,14,19,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
}
.logo{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;letter-spacing:0.02em;
}
.logo-status{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;
  font-size:10px;color:var(--green);letter-spacing:.06em;
}
.logo-status::before{
  content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);
  animation:blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}
nav{display:flex;gap:2px}
.nav-btn{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.05em;
  padding:4px 11px;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid transparent;
  background:transparent;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all .16s;
}
.nav-btn:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border2);background:var(--bg2)}
.header-right{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.04em}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{
  padding:72px 40px 64px;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 340px;gap:64px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.hero-glow{
  position:absolute;width:500px;height:500px;border-radius:50%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(249,115,22,0.07) 0%,transparent 70%);
  top:-150px;right:-80px;pointer-events:none;
}
.hero-pre{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--orange);letter-spacing:.1em;
  text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:18px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
}
.hero-pre::before{content:'$';color:var(--muted)}
h1{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:600;
  font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,52px);
  line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.02em;
  color:#ffffff;margin-bottom:20px;
}
h1 .hl{color:var(--orange)}
h1 .cursor{
  display:inline-block;width:3px;height:.9em;
  background:var(--orange);margin-left:3px;vertical-align:middle;
  animation:cursor 1.1s step-end infinite;
}
@keyframes cursor{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}
.hero-desc{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;max-width:500px;margin-bottom:36px}
.cta-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cta-main{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:10px 20px;border-radius:5px;
  background:var(--orange);color:#0c0e13;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:600;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.04em;
  border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;text-transform:uppercase;
}
.cta-main:hover{background:var(--orange2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.cta-ghost{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);
  padding:10px 18px;border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:5px;
  background:transparent;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.04em;
  transition:all .18s;
}
.cta-ghost:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--orange-border)}

/* pipeline preview */
.pipeline{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.pip-row{
  display:flex;align-items:stretch;gap:0;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:10px 0;cursor:pointer;
  transition:background .15s;border-radius:4px;padding:10px 12px;
}
.pip-row:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.pip-icon{
  width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:4px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:600;
  flex-shrink:0;margin-right:12px;align-self:center;
}
.pip-meta{flex:1;min-width:0}
.pip-name{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);line-height:1.3}
.pip-dur{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
.pip-badge{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;
  letter-spacing:.05em;align-self:center;flex-shrink:0;
}

/* ── PIPELINE PROGRESS BAR ── */
.pipe-bar{
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:0 40px;background:var(--bg1);
  display:flex;align-items:stretch;
  overflow-x:auto;
}
.pipe-bar::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.pipe-stage{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0;flex-shrink:0;cursor:pointer;
  transition:background .15s;
}
.pipe-stage:hover .ps-inner{background:var(--bg3)}
.ps-inner{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:14px 18px;transition:background .15s;
}
.ps-num{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.06em}
.ps-name{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap}
.pipe-stage.active .ps-name{color:var(--orange)}
.pipe-stage.active .ps-num{color:var(--orange)}
.pipe-arrow{
  width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--faint);
  position:relative;flex-shrink:0;
}
.pipe-arrow::after{
  content:'';position:absolute;right:-4px;top:-3px;
  width:0;height:0;
  border-left:5px solid var(--faint);
  border-top:4px solid transparent;
  border-bottom:4px solid transparent;
}

/* ── TWO COLUMN BODY ── */
.body-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:240px 1fr;min-height:100vh}

/* ── SIDEBAR ── */
.sidebar{
  border-right:1px solid var(--border);
  position:sticky;top:56px;height:calc(100vh - 56px);
  overflow-y:auto;padding:24px 0;background:var(--bg);
}
.sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.sb-label{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--faint);padding:0 24px;margin-bottom:10px;
}
.sb-item{
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  padding:8px 24px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
  border-left:2px solid transparent;
}
.sb-item:hover{background:var(--bg2)}
.sb-item.active{
  border-left-color:var(--orange);
  background:var(--orange-bg);
}
.sb-item.active .sb-name{color:var(--orange)}
.sb-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.sb-name{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);transition:color .15s}
.sb-dur{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:2px}
.sb-divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin:14px 24px}
.sb-foot{
  padding:12px 24px;
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--faint);line-height:1.8;letter-spacing:.04em
}

/* ── MAIN ── */
.main{min-width:0}
.phase-block{padding:48px 48px 56px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.phase-block:last-child{border-bottom:none}

.phase-header{margin-bottom:28px}
.ph-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
.ph-tag{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:600;
  padding:3px 8px;border-radius:3px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;
  border:1px solid;
}
.ph-divider{flex:1;height:1px;background:var(--border)}
.ph-dur{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.04em}
.ph-title{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;
  letter-spacing:-.02em;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;
  display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;
}
.ph-title-color{}
.ph-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;max-width:600px}

/* cards */
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}
.card{
  background:var(--bg1);border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .16s;
}
.card:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.card.open{border-color:var(--orange-border)}
.card-head{padding:16px 18px 14px;cursor:pointer}
.card-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:10px}
.card-led{
  width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;
  position:relative;
}
/* pulse ring on open */
.card.open .card-led::after{
  content:'';position:absolute;inset:-3px;border-radius:50%;
  border:1px solid;border-color:inherit;opacity:.4;
  animation:ring .9s ease-out infinite;
}
@keyframes ring{0%{transform:scale(1);opacity:.4}100%{transform:scale(2);opacity:0}}
.card-title{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text)}
.card-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px}
.card-tag{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.04em;
  padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;border:1px solid;
}
/* expand */
.card-body{
  overflow:hidden;max-height:0;
  transition:max-height .35s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
}
.card.open .card-body{max-height:600px}
.card-inner{
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:16px 18px;
  background:var(--bg2);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;
}
.ci-section{}
.ci-label{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:8px;
}
.ci-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
.ci-list li{
  font-size:12px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;
  display:flex;gap:7px;align-items:baseline;
}
.ci-list li::before{content:'>';font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--orange);font-size:10px;flex-shrink:0}
.card-foot{
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:9px 18px;
  background:var(--bg2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
}
.toggle-txt{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);cursor:pointer;transition:color .15s}
.toggle-txt:hover{color:var(--text)}
.card.open .open-txt{display:none}
.card:not(.open) .close-txt{display:none}
.plan-btn{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.04em;
  padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;
  border:1px solid var(--orange-border);background:var(--orange-bg);
  color:var(--orange);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;
}
.plan-btn:hover{background:rgba(249,115,22,.15);border-color:var(--orange)}

/* ── STATS BAR ── */
.stats-bar{
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  background:var(--bg1);
}
.stat{
  padding:24px 32px;border-right:1px solid var(--border);
}
.stat:last-child{border-right:none}
.stat-n{
  font-family:var(--mono);font-size:28px;font-weight:600;
  color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;
}
.stat-l{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:32px 40px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  background:var(--bg1);
}
.foot-l{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.03em}
.foot-r{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:.05em}

/* ── ANIM ── */
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.fu{animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.fu1{animation-delay:.05s}.fu2{animation-delay:.1s}.fu3{animation-delay:.15s}.fu4{animation-delay:.2s}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:900px){
  .body-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .sidebar{display:none}
  .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:48px 24px;gap:40px}
  .pipeline{display:none}
  header{padding:0 20px}
  .phase-block{padding:36px 24px}
  .cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  footer{padding:24px 20px;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;text-align:center}
  .pipe-bar{padding:0 24px}
}
@media(max-width:480px){
  .card-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .stats-bar{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  h1{font-size:26px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="site">

<a href="/resources" class="back-btn">← Back to Resources</a>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <div class="logo">
    <span>ops.map</span>
    <span class="logo-status">pipeline running</span>
  </div>
  <nav id="topNav"></nav>
  <div class="header-right">8 phases&nbsp;·&nbsp;~18 months</div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div>
    <div class="hero-pre">init roadmap --track devops-cloud</div>
    <h1>Ship faster.<br/>Break nothing.<br/><span class="hl">Own the pipeline.</span><span class="cursor"></span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">A structured path from Linux basics to Kubernetes, CI/CD, IaC, observability, and cloud-native architecture. Built for engineers who want to deploy with confidence.</p>
    <div class="cta-row">
      <button class="cta-main" onclick="document.getElementById('phase-0').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        ./start.sh
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 6h8M6 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
      </button>
      <button class="cta-ghost" onclick="document.getElementById('phase-0').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">view phases</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pipeline" id="heroPipeline"></div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat fu fu1"><div class="stat-n">8</div><div class="stat-l">Learning phases</div></div>
  <div class="stat fu fu2"><div class="stat-n">~18mo</div><div class="stat-l">Full timeline</div></div>
  <div class="stat fu fu3"><div class="stat-n">32+</div><div class="stat-l">Core topics</div></div>
  <div class="stat fu fu4"><div class="stat-n">90+</div><div class="stat-l">Tools & resources</div></div>
</div>

<!-- PIPELINE BAR -->
<div class="pipe-bar" id="pipeBar"></div>

<!-- BODY -->
<div class="body-wrap">
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="sb-label">Phases</div>
    <div id="sidebarInner"></div>
    <div class="sb-divider"></div>
    <div class="sb-foot">
      Linux → Networking<br/>
      → Git → Docker<br/>
      → CI/CD → K8s<br/>
      → Cloud → SRE
    </div>
  </aside>
  <main id="mainArea"></main>
</div>

<footer>
  <div class="foot-l">ops.map — DevOps & Cloud Roadmap 2025</div>
  <div class="foot-r">Linux · Docker · K8s · Terraform · AWS · GitHub Actions · Prometheus · ArgoCD</div>
</footer>

</div>
<script>
const PHASES = [
  {
    id:0, label:"Linux & OS fundamentals", short:"linux",
    color:"#22c55e", tagColor:"rgba(34,197,94,.15)", tagBorder:"rgba(34,197,94,.3)",
    dur:"3–4 weeks", status:"PASS",
    desc:"Every DevOps tool runs on Linux. If you skip this, you will suffer forever. Learn to be comfortable in a terminal before touching any cloud service.",
    cards:[
      {title:"Linux basics", tags:["bash","filesystem","processes"],
       learn:["File system hierarchy (/etc, /var, /proc)","User & group permissions (chmod, chown)","Process management (ps, top, kill, systemd)","Package managers (apt, yum, dnf)","Shell scripting fundamentals"],
       res:["The Linux Command Line (Shotts, free)","OverTheWire: Bandit wargame","Linux Journey (linuxjourney.com)"]},
      {title:"Networking essentials", tags:["TCP/IP","DNS","SSH","firewalls"],
       learn:["OSI model & TCP/IP stack","DNS resolution step by step","SSH key auth, tunneling, port forwarding","iptables & nftables firewall rules","curl, netstat, ss, tcpdump, nmap"],
       res:["Computer Networking: A Top-Down Approach","TryHackMe Linux & Networking paths","Beej's Guide to Network Programming (free)"]},
      {title:"Storage & filesystems", tags:["LVM","RAID","NFS"],
       learn:["Disk partitioning (fdisk, parted)","LVM: physical volumes, VGs, LVs","Filesystem types: ext4, xfs, btrfs","Mount, fstab, swap configuration","NFS and SMB basics"],
       res:["Red Hat storage docs","Digital Ocean tutorials","Linux Filesystem Hierarchy Standard"]},
      {title:"Shell scripting", tags:["bash","cron","automation"],
       learn:["Variables, conditionals, loops in bash","Functions & error handling (set -e, -u)","Cron jobs & at scheduler","Text processing: awk, sed, grep, jq","Writing idempotent maintenance scripts"],
       res:["Advanced Bash-Scripting Guide (free)","ShellCheck linter","Google Shell Style Guide"]},
    ]
  },
  {
    id:1, label:"Version control & Git", short:"git",
    color:"#f97316", tagColor:"rgba(249,115,22,.15)", tagBorder:"rgba(249,115,22,.3)",
    dur:"1–2 weeks", status:"PASS",
    desc:"Git is not optional. As a DevOps engineer you'll use it to version infrastructure, pipelines, configs, and code — often in the same repo.",
    cards:[
      {title:"Git internals", tags:["commits","branches","rebasing"],
       learn:["Objects: blobs, trees, commits, tags","HEAD, refs, and the reflog","Branching strategies (GitFlow, trunk-based)","Interactive rebase & cherry-pick","Stash, bisect, worktrees"],
       res:["Pro Git (Chacon & Straub, free)","Git Internals (YouTube — Linus Torvalds talk)","Oh Shit, Git!?! (ohshitgit.com)"]},
      {title:"Collaboration workflows", tags:["PRs","code review","hooks"],
       learn:["Pull requests & code review etiquette","Branch protection rules","Git hooks (pre-commit, commit-msg)","Monorepo vs polyrepo tradeoffs","Signed commits & GPG"],
       res:["GitHub Docs","Atlassian Git tutorials","Conventional Commits spec"]},
    ]
  },
  {
    id:2, label:"Containers & Docker", short:"docker",
    color:"#38bdf8", tagColor:"rgba(56,189,248,.15)", tagBorder:"rgba(56,189,248,.3)",
    dur:"3–4 weeks", status:"PASS",
    desc:"Containers changed how software is packaged and run. Docker is the lingua franca — understand it deeply before layering Kubernetes on top.",
    cards:[
      {title:"Docker fundamentals", tags:["images","containers","layers"],
       learn:["Dockerfile instructions & layer caching","Union filesystems (overlayfs)","Container lifecycle (create/start/stop/rm)","Volumes vs bind mounts vs tmpfs","Networking: bridge, host, none, overlay"],
       res:["Docker official docs","Play with Docker (free sandbox)","TechWorld with Nana Docker tutorial"]},
      {title:"Dockerfile best practices", tags:["multi-stage","security","size"],
       learn:["Multi-stage builds for tiny images","Non-root users in containers",".dockerignore & build context hygiene","Layer ordering for cache efficiency","Scanning with Docker Scout / Trivy"],
       res:["Docker best practices guide","Hadolint Dockerfile linter","Snyk container scanning docs"]},
      {title:"Docker Compose", tags:["services","networking","local dev"],
       learn:["Defining multi-container apps","Service dependencies & health checks","Environment variables & .env files","Override files for env-specific configs","Profiles for optional services"],
       res:["Docker Compose docs","Awesome Compose (github examples)","Earthly blog on Compose patterns"]},
      {title:"Container registries", tags:["ECR","GCR","GHCR"],
       learn:["Pushing/pulling images & tagging strategy","Docker Hub rate limits & alternatives","GitHub Container Registry (GHCR) setup","AWS ECR authentication with IRSA","Image signing with Cosign & Notary"],
       res:["AWS ECR docs","GHCR docs","Sigstore / Cosign docs"]},
    ]
  },
  {
